    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Build, and survive.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Construct your camp into a fortified base. Venture out into the wasteland to scavenge supplies, find unique building blueprints, and come across new weapons to take back to your stronghold. Upgrade your fortifications to withstand the elements, and to defend yourself from the nasty creatures that the world throws at you.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>How long can you survive for?</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Chronicles: Wasteland Assault features a survival mode; a classic survival shooter that goes back to a familiar formula of how a wave-by-wave shooter should be. Join this developing community and be a part of a growing, and expanding world that takes place in the same universe as the hit books, written by Tyee ‘Lar Oxenbury. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Constant free updates.</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >TC:WA is a free game, and is constantly being worked on with new content and features. Participate in this expanding development, leave your input, share your thoughts, and watch how this game will be tailored towards players who are just as passionate as the development team itself. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Feel the power, slay them all.</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every weapon has their strengths. You'll surely find one that you'll love. Upgrade your arsenal with attachments to further push the boundaries on how far you can survive for. Experiment with different perks, strengthen their effects by stacking them multiple times. </p>",
